{"tid":1601954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係林鄭答問會，紅衫巴打","createTime":"2019-09-29T08:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T16:20:38.000Z","uid":138248,"like":280,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d0164628329c13c8deb81c0eadbfeeb595f09a1d","tid":1601954,"uid":138248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"今朝先睇返連登留言，想分享下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果日其實都怕怕地唔想去，入場時過安檢係有三四十個黑西裝人招呼我一個，入到場後面見到咁L多cam man 先知直播，我又無其他人準備得咁足，聽前幾個絲打發言勁高質我當堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxBWaSW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxBWaSW.png&h=52c8c8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但無理由黎咗唔講架，點都放紙入箱抽<br />\n<br />\n仲有以下幾點想回應:<br />\n<br />\n點解着紅衫？<br />\n真係好傷心，我哋啲30尾嘅大叔，平時係大減價先買衫，一着就五至十年，polo最平就係你d 無人着嘅色。我飲衫嚟㗎喎，俾人話真傷心<br />\n<br />\n無組織？<br />\n其實我無準備講稿，知道抽中都係問週邊d朋友有咩想同林鄭講，同真坳底<br />\n<br />\n點解唔屌柒林鄭？<br />\n其實真係有諗過，當時就係想抽中三分鐘自由時間顏射佢，但去到現場，會發覺好多都係同路人，好嬲但都好忍耐，如果發茅小柒佢，只會輸人兼輸陣，呢個係當時嘅感覺。出黎效果大家都係睇到佢無回應，如果佢要再做，都會同一效果，民意佢都係輸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veD8GL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veD8GL.png&h=6d6eb088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同你擰轉頭見到成埋記者做直播，我真心覺得坐响度無瀨尿就應該可以攞英勇勳章，大家亦都唔好屌人型蜈蚣師兄，起碼人哋敢發聲露面。<br />\n<br />\n叫林女士？<br />\n<br />\n我又唔太想叫佢林特首，叫女士無咩問題。<br />\n<br />\n我明好多爸絲睇唔起個活動，但不能否認它好入屋，如果三十個發言嘅都係支持政府嘅，咁咪又好似四點鐘記招，聽埋d丫理。總之兄弟爬山，各自響自己覺得有能力去做嘅地方努力啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實無咩野講，噢最後我老婆煮野好好食，只係有時過於健康，你明啦。"},{"pid":"148ec42eda3b3d0b5f80e18c64f5f6e7a94dfeec","tid":1601954,"uid":36722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好好啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4757a03fa2cc600f3708d89debb34e1df2742fcf","tid":1601954,"uid":222048,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"巴打是咪比老婆捉上黎澄清佢煮野好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ec9d796d5ae26fa5520381367c7a1a27911328","tid":1601954,"uid":300542,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"林女士叫得好"},{"pid":"dceb535babfe4d4cb7ca1861c2568e117a4f161a","tid":1601954,"uid":138248,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"148ec42eda3b3d0b5f80e18c64f5f6e7a94dfeec","tid":1601954,"uid":36722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好好啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"壓力來源，行入黎無帶面罩，一言一行都影響一家"},{"pid":"eaaca7144c78bdadbe86b8471c02bc39e0a1d3eb","tid":1601954,"uid":138248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16ec9d796d5ae26fa5520381367c7a1a27911328","tid":1601954,"uid":300542,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"林女士叫得好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"唔係，我都唔知可以叫乜，要不失尊重。"},{"pid":"a73e25d84f79520a75f9d026974ae61abae6e97c","tid":1601954,"uid":284304,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"其實同佢對話姐係認受佢既統治<br />\n佢根本無資格出黎對話"},{"pid":"ca038ef9373b9836caa78fd3a98a961f3fc87be6","tid":1601954,"uid":324266,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"你係我全晚最中意果個 感謝你"},{"pid":"d471373a64c815fb8dcdc45f6eb087890da421c1","tid":1601954,"